\series bold
The following shortcomings are observed when it comes to the application
 of DWT to fault detection: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
All methods except the one in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Perera2011"

\end_inset

 uses voltages for classification.
 CVT attenuates all high frequencies beyond 200 Hz effectively making the
 voltage signal unusable
\end_layout

